OL,3,C#10,000 reward for safe return of
OL,4,Cmissing Cocker Spaniel Mabel
OL,6,FThe desperate owners of a missing dog
OL,7,Fare offering a #10,000 reward for her
OL,8,Fsafe return, after she disappeared
OL,9,Ffrom their farm in Lancashire.
OL,11,FMabel, an 18-month-old Cocker Spaniel,
OL,12,Fwas last seen at their farm in Inskip
OL,13,Fon the Friday 10 April.
OL,15,FDrones with thermal imaging were
OL,16,Fbrought in to help search for her and
OL,17,FLancashire Police say they are
OL,18,Finvestigating.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
