OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777561869
OL,3,C#10,000 reward for safe return of
OL,4,Cmissing Cocker Spaniel Mabel
OL,6,FHer owners, Sarah and Paul Livesey
OL,7,Ffear a visitor to their farm shop may
OL,8,Fhave stolen her for breeding.
OL,10,FOwner Sarah Livesey said: "She is the
OL,11,Fmost loving loyal dog, she is
OL,12,Fliterally the centre of our family.
OL,14,F"The children are devastated, we are
OL,15,Fall devastated.
OL,17,F"We just miss her so much and I know
OL,18,Fhow much she will miss us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777561869
OL,3,C#10,000 reward for safe return of
OL,4,Cmissing Cocker Spaniel Mabel
OL,6,FThe family have had Mabel since she
OL,7,Fwas a puppy. She has been described as
OL,8,Fred with a white chest and a wrinkly
OL,9,Fforehead.
OL,11,FThere have been many possible
OL,12,Fsightings, all of which the family
OL,13,Fhave followed up, but none have turned
OL,14,Fout to be Mabel.
OL,16,FSarah hopes the reward, raised with
OL,17,Fhelp from the wider family, will
OL,18,Fencourage someone to come forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
