OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777561869
OL,3,C#10,000 reward for safe return of
OL,4,Cmissing Cocker Spaniel Mabel
OL,6,F"I can't sleep, I'm just existing, I'm
OL,7,Fhere in body but I'm definitely not
OL,8,Fhere in person," she said.
OL,10,F"I don't care about the money, I don't
OL,11,Fcare about anything, I just need her
OL,12,Fhome."
OL,14,FIt is believed around 2,000 dogs are
OL,15,Fstolen in the UK every year with the
OL,16,FNorth West one of the highest risk
OL,17,Fareas.
OL,19,FStealing a dog is now a specific
OL,20,Fcriminal offence and perpetrators can
OL,21,Fbe jailed for up to five years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
