PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777561869
OL,3,C#10,000 reward for safe return of
OL,4,Cmissing Cocker Spaniel Mabel
OL,6,FLisa Eardley, centre manager at the
OL,7,FDogs Trust Manchester, said: "I don't
OL,8,Fthink they consider the impact it has
OL,9,Fon families when they steal these dogs.
OL,11,F"It's an easy way to make money and
OL,12,Fit's quite quick and you can move dogs
OL,13,Fquite quickly and sadly this is the
OL,14,Freality we are in at the moment,
OL,15,Fespecially what we call cute breeds.
OL,17,F"They tend to be the ones that they go
OL,18,Ffor more but i think generally its
OL,19,Fbecause they can be moved quite
OL,20,Fquickly and they can make a lot of
OL,21,Fmoney. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
